title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - Airplane review - local legend 14 The Bell 47J Ranger
description:
The first local legend of the year is for the first time ever something different: a helicopter. In this case the Bell 74J Ranger which comes in two variants: as normal helicopter and one with floats so you can use the helicopter almost everywhere around the world.

0:00 intro
0:10 review of different types and liveries
2:40 detailed review of exterior and interior
